{"tid":844414,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"放假行山紀錄","createTime":"2018-10-02T00:48:24.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-17T08:21:36.000Z","uid":32786,"like":5,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"138ea76a83457b7992c3e44b4ce9051d576697fb","tid":844414,"uid":32786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T00:48:24.000Z","msg":"話說我放假97%機會率行山 （keep左年幾）連續放幾多日就行幾多日 <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n國慶呢幾日有感 做個紀錄比自己睇 <br />\n<br />\n星期六半日假就行4個鐘內 全日就5小時<br />\n基本上大部分都係5小時內完成 <br />\n走既地方一定有車搭<br />\n<br />\n29/09/2018 13:30-17:00<br />\n<br />\n荃灣愉景新城&mdash;石龍拱&mdash;田夫仔&mdash;大棠&mdash;行出元朗市中心<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n30/9/2018 07:50-12:10<br />\n<br />\n大埔富亨邨&mdash;九龍坑山&mdash;鶴藪水塘&mdash;黃嶺&mdash;八仙嶺&mdash;大尾督巴士總站<br />\n<br />\n01/10/2018 7:20-12:00<br />\n<br />\n東涌映灣園二期&mdash;白芒&mdash;婆髻山&mdash;大東山&mdash;伯公坳&mdash;石門甲&mdash;逸東邨巴士總站<br />\n<br />\n歡迎大家分享下路線 港島就未行過 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"582921b99086e6c2b936a1fa32693ac335ae7b9e","tid":844414,"uid":25357,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T00:50:22.000Z","msg":"今日行你最後果條，白芒上蓮花，不過未決定三條路簡邊條落山"},{"pid":"2d6d0031e28353e427942144dd625d2742048bf9","tid":844414,"uid":32786,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"582921b99086e6c2b936a1fa32693ac335ae7b9e","tid":844414,"uid":25357,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T00:50:22.000Z","msg":"今日行你最後果條，白芒上蓮花，不過未決定三條路簡邊條落山"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T00:51:23.000Z","msg":"黃龍坑落山有點驚險 伯公最正路  第三路係？"},{"pid":"c8ada0005d05a70ac48dc6dcc8282b64ed06aecb","tid":844414,"uid":25357,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2d6d0031e28353e427942144dd625d2742048bf9","tid":844414,"uid":32786,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"582921b99086e6c2b936a1fa32693ac335ae7b9e","tid":844414,"uid":25357,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,